T1  - From Homogenization to Pluralism: International Management Research in the Academy and Beyond
AU  - Tsui, Anne S.
Y1  - 2007/12/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amj.2007.28166121
DO  - 10.5465/amj.2007.28166121
